title: 820-00281 not boot just shows battery symbol
message:
820-00281-A board came in dead condition.
when disconnected battery and plugged adapter fan spin and shows a battery symbol then off.
PPBUS G3H =12.5 volt
PP3V3 S5 = 3.3  
5V S4 = 5 /PPVCC CPU =0.6Vwhen powering up
